OL,3,CNottingham's Splendour Festival will
OL,4,Cbe axed after almost 20 years
OL,6,FOne of the most iconic annual music
OL,7,Ffestivals in the East Midlands will be
OL,8,Faxed after this year's event.
OL,10,FBands will play at the Splendour
OL,11,FFestival in Nottingham's Wollaton Park
OL,12,Ffor the final time next month as it
OL,13,Fcomes to an end after 18 years.
OL,15,FOrganisers say the cost of staging
OL,16,Fevents has risen sharply as people
OL,17,Fhave started spending less on going
OL,18,Fout to watch live music.
