OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782587893
OL,3,CNottingham's Splendour Festival will
OL,4,Cbe axed after almost 20 years
OL,6,FThey also say the festival market has
OL,7,Fbecome much more crowded with lots of
OL,8,Fcompetition for people's limited
OL,9,Fbudgets.
OL,11,FAlong with being one of the country's
OL,12,Fmost popular festivals, Splendour has
OL,13,Falso been a longstanding champion of
OL,14,FNottingham's music scene.
OL,16,FThe city's own Jake Bugg headlined the
OL,17,Ffestival in 2014 when he was 20, and
OL,18,Fmore recently, rock duo ALT BLK ERA
OL,19,Fperformed after winning the Future
OL,20,FSound of Nottingham.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
