CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782587893
OL,3,CNottingham's Splendour Festival will
OL,4,Cbe axed after almost 20 years
OL,6,FOver the years, hundreds of local
OL,7,Fartists have taken to its stages,
OL,8,Fperforming alongside national acts and
OL,9,Fwinning over new audiences.
OL,11,FNottingham-based independent music
OL,12,Fpromoter DHP Family MD George Akins
OL,13,Fsaid, "We're really proud of
OL,14,FSplendour. It has truly played an
OL,15,Fimportant part in the lives of many
OL,16,Fpeople, and is much loved for its
OL,17,Ffamily-friendly environment, as well
OL,18,Fas its genre and era-spanning line-ups
OL,19,Fthat have seen some huge artists come
OL,20,Fto play in Wollaton Park.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
