PN,34804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782587893
OL,3,CNottingham's Splendour Festival will
OL,4,Cbe axed after almost 20 years
OL,6,F"Thanks to everyone for your loyalty
OL,7,Fand support over the years, we
OL,8,Fcouldn't have done it without you."
OL,10,FThe last Splendour Festival will take
OL,11,Fplace on 18 July with artists like The
OL,12,FWombats, Primal Scream, Craig David
OL,13,Fand Snow Patrol performing.
OL,15,FFestival organisers said: "We've loved
OL,16,Fbringing Splendour to you since 2008.
OL,17,FWe know how special it is to this
OL,18,Fcommunity. We want to let you know
OL,19,Fupfront that this will be the last
OL,20,Fone, so we can celebrate together in
OL,21,Fstyle."
OL,26,@wD@[OU
