OL,3,CNottingham's Splendour Festival will
OL,4,Cbe axed after almost 20 years
OL,6,FLeader of Nottingham City Council,
OL,7,FCllr Neghat Khan, said: "We're proud
OL,8,Fto have helped develop Splendour into
OL,9,Fa Nottingham institution since its
OL,10,Finception in 2008.
OL,12,F"The festival has showcased an
OL,13,Fincredible breadth of talent ` from
OL,14,Femerging Nottingham artists who went
OL,15,Fon to achieve great success, to
OL,16,Finternationally renowned performers.
OL,18,F"Beyond the music, it created a
OL,19,Fjoyful, welcoming, and family-friendly
OL,20,Fatmosphere, where countless Nottingham
OL,21,Fresidents made lasting memories.
OL,26,@oD@YOUzD@AOU
