PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782587893
OL,3,CNottingham's Splendour Festival will
OL,4,Cbe axed after almost 20 years
OL,6,F"We hope now that many of you will
OL,7,Fturn out to say goodbye and make this
OL,8,Ffinal festival a fitting celebration
OL,9,Fof Splendour's legacy in Nottingham."
